snippet.title: Amber Heard on 'Aquaman', Hollywood abuse allegations and more (November 15, 2017)
snippet.description:
Star of the upcoming Aquaman film and internationally acclaimed actress Amber Heard stunned as she arrived on the Red Carpet to accept her award GQ's Woman of the Year for 2017. 
She recounts how she found out Australia had voted 'Yes' on same sex marriage.
@GQ Australia
